PewterCity_Gym_Text_BrockIntro::
    .string "So, you made it here.\n"
    .string "I am BROCK, License D Examiner.\p"
    .string "This test is not about style.\n"
    .string "It is about discipline.\p"
    .string "My BRAINROTS are steady\n"
    .string "like stone.\p"
    .string "If your team loses focus,\n"
    .string "this exam ends fast.\p"
    .string "Fine, candidate.\n"
    .string "Show me your best!{PLAY_BGM}{MUS_ENCOUNTER_GYM_LEADER}$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_BrockDefeat::
    .string "You held your focus.\p"
    .string "As proof of your victory,\n"
    .string "I grant you the official\l"
    .string "LICENSE D STONEBADGE.\p"
    .string "{FONT_NORMAL}{PLAYER} received the STONEBADGE\n"
    .string "from BROCK!{PAUSE_MUSIC}{PLAY_BGM}{MUS_OBTAIN_BADGE}{PAUSE 0xFE}{PAUSE 0x56}{RESUME_MUSIC}\p"
    .string "{FONT_MALE}With the STONEBADGE, your\n"
    .string "BRAINROTS obey stronger commands.\p"
    .string "It also enables FLASH\n"
    .string "outside battle.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_TakeThisWithYou::
    .string "Wait.\n"
    .string "Take this with you.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_ReceivedTM39FromBrock::
    .string "{PLAYER} received TM39\n"
    .string "from BROCK.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_ExplainTM39::
    .string "A TM teaches a technique\n"
    .string "to a BRAINROT.\p"
    .string "A TM works only once,\n"
    .string "so choose carefully.\p"
    .string "TM39 contains ROCK TOMB.\p"
    .string "It drops stone pressure\n"
    .string "on the foe and lowers SPEED.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_BrockPostBattle::
    .string "There are many candidates\n"
    .string "in Kanto.\p"
    .string "You have unusual focus.\p"
    .string "Go east toward MOON NOISE CAVE.\n"
    .string "Your next test waits there.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_DontHaveRoomForThis::
    .string "You do not have room for this.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_LiamIntro::
    .string "Stop right there, candidate!\p"
    .string "You are still far from\n"
    .string "passing BROCK's D test!$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_LiamDefeat::
    .string "Darn!\p"
    .string "Distance is not the same\n"
    .string "as readiness!$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_LiamPostBattle::
    .string "You are steady.\n"
    .string "But BROCK is steadier.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_LetMeTakeYouToTheTop::
    .string "Hiya!\n"
    .string "Taking the License D exam?\p"
    .string "I am no examiner, but I\n"
    .string "can give advice.\p"
    .string "Want help with the test?$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_LetsGetHappening::
    .string "All right!\n"
    .string "Let us get focused!$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_TryDifferentPartyOrders::
    .string "The first BRAINROT out\n"
    .string "is the leftmost in your list.\p"
    .string "Change order to match\n"
    .string "the examiner's team.$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_ItsFreeLetsGetHappening::
    .string "It is free advice!\n"
    .string "Let us get focused!$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_YoureChampMaterial::
    .string "Just as I thought!\n"
    .string "You have Class S potential!$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_GymStatue::
    .string "LICENSE D EXAM HALL\n"
    .string "EXAMINER: BROCK\p"
    .string "PASSED CANDIDATES:\n"
    .string "{RIVAL}$"

PewterCity_Gym_Text_GymStatuePlayerWon::
    .string "LICENSE D EXAM HALL\n"
    .string "EXAMINER: BROCK\p"
    .string "PASSED CANDIDATES:\n"
    .string "{RIVAL}, {PLAYER}$"
